projects.name: Personality prediction through CV, using NLP and ML models
projects.description: Developed a system that offers a unique approach to predicting individuals' personalities by analyzing various factors based on the Big Five Personality Traits. The system leverages logistic regression for model training, it utilizes the pyresparser module, empowered by the NLTK and spaCy libraries in Python, to extract relevant data points from resumes.

projects.name: Deciphering Deception, Deepfake audio detection using LSTM deep learning model
projects.description: Developed and proposed LSTM model to classify real and computer generated audios. Discussed how different hyperparameters affect the results. Four models were tested with four different optimizers each to conclude the best model and optimizer for deepfake audio detection.

projects.name: Music Recommendation system, using ML algorithms
projects.description: Created a music recommendation system that provides users with a personalized listening experience using algorithms like K mean clustering and PCA. Evaluated the effectiveness of the system using metrics such as precision, recall, and F1 score.
